{"word":"λάβρος","slug":"λάβρος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λάβρος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b> of wind, rain, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>, <i>furious, boisterous</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>λ. πῦρ, κύματα, πόντος</el>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>after <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, of men, <i>boisterous, turbulent, violent</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>greedy</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>λάβρως</el>, <i>violently, furiously</i>, <b><a href='S:Theognis'>Theogn.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>greedily</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}